On this post I share a link to a dashboard depicting the fuel prices thoughout the Brazil. The dataset used to generate the plots is provided by the brazillian government through ANP (Agência Nacional do Petróleo, Gás Natural e Biocombustíveis). Follows the link to the actual dashboard page: here.
@jonathanborba
The dashboard is WIP and at the moment tries to address three questions: How do fuel prices vary, in average, among distributors?
